.SH NAME
dev_change_xdp_fd \- set or clear a bpf program for a device rx path
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" dev_change_xdp_fd
.BI "(struct net_device *dev "  ","
.BI "struct netlink_ext_ack *extack "  ","
.BI "int fd "  ","
.BI "int expected_fd "  ","
.BI "u32 flags "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
device
.IP "extack" 12
netlink extended ack
.IP "fd" 12
new program fd or negative value to clear
.IP "expected_fd" 12
old program fd that userspace expects to replace or clear
.IP "flags" 12
xdp-related flags

Set or clear a bpf program for a device
